{
  "stem": "12491.1",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "We had to divide into groups, some earning money in one way or the other, and others, working on the farm.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "I was-- I and two other fellows were assigned to do business in-- in the city, in the big city, which was Lwow.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "L-W-O-- apostrophe-- W.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "We were going to Lwow, carrying various farm products.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "Not only from our farm, but also organized-- which is the word which was used at that time-- for stealing and-- and/or buying, and carrying it to the city for sale.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "The stuff consisted of chickens, live or dead, turkeys, live or dead, and cheeses, kielbasi, et cetera.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "One-- one situation was where we carried a sack full of live chickens into the city.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "And it was getting rather late in the evening.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "We knocked on different doors in the Jewish section.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 51,
      "text": "And we tried to sell them.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 52,
      "text": "And I remember one lady said to me, well, I would buy one.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 53,
      "text": "But you would have to kill it for me.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 54,
      "text": "So I said, well, no choice.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 55,
      "text": "Give me a knife.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 56,
      "text": "She gave me a knife.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 57,
      "text": "She opened the door to the back stairway.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 58,
      "text": "I stepped on the chicken's head, and cut it.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 59,
      "text": "I cut off his neck.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 60,
      "text": "Maybe it's not pleasant to listen to these things.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 61,
      "text": "But there will be worse than that.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, I was not in danger just going to the city.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was in danger with my activities in the city.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Selling goods, even-- even food, was forbidden.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Food was only available on ration cards.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And as a matter of fact, there was, at one time, a situation where I bought a large amount-- I think 100 pounds of Polish kielbasi.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we divided it among the three of us.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
